{"tid":727534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學校家長群組最啱！WhatsApp 新增消息發佈功能","createTime":"2018-07-03T05:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T12:30:13.000Z","uid":20815,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cfe7a21cc65642d6f94b323dd9da33c74cc82f","tid":727534,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp 不斷改進群組功能的用戶體驗，加入了好些新功能，例如群組描述，亦容許用戶在離開後重新被加回。日前 WhatsApp 再宣布另一針對群組的全新功能，讓群組管理員可以單方向發佈訊息。有別於我們慣常以群組去溝通聊天，管理員只要將發佈消息功能啟動，其他群組內的成員就不可以發帖或回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/0702-2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F0702-2a.jpg&h=1290efb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp 表示有很多用戶，例如學校、社區中心或非牟利組織的老師和家長，都會使用群組功能發佈重要的訊息和資訊，有了這個發佈消息的功能後，其他群組成員就無法發帖騷擾到他人，或者將無關的訊息傳到群組內。類似的消息發佈功能在 WhatsApp 的競爭對手 Telegram 早就存在，容許用戶建立群組或頻道，後者正正就是只有管理員一方可以將訊息廣播。<br />\n<br />\n要使用 WhatsApp 的最新發佈消息功能，首先要確定使用最新的軟件版本，群組管理員點擊 Group Info，然後再選擇 Group Settings &gt; Send Messages，最後選擇 Only Admins 即可。<br />\n<br />\n來源：ubergizmo<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/02/whatsapp-new-group-broadcast-feature/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2Fwhatsapp-new-group-broadcast-feature%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=Nyti4CReHsaybVxJJYr7HNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=eae7b07c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/02/whatsapp-new-group-broadcast-feature/software/android-app/</a>"},{"pid":"4c11cde7e7b554a4d6009b6a6ce061dbf9e4e61c","tid":727534,"uid":20815,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"我淨係諗起HJ2Q <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e019f6420b00e3e89204fb21151491554da3826","tid":727534,"uid":895